cosmic-radio (0.1.0-1) noble; urgency=medium

  * Initial release for Pop OS.
  * Internet radio streaming applet for the COSMIC desktop.
  * Station management via TOML configuration.
  * Now-playing metadata display and artwork caching.
  * PLS playlist support and "Play from URL" feature.

